Name: Warrior Paint - 2005 GOTY Edition
About the game: Warrior Paint delivers the gritty realism and cinematic intensity of World War II's epic battlefield moments like never before - through the eyes of citizen soldiers and unsung heroes from an alliance of countries who together helped shape the course of modern history. Warrior Paint is an intense story-driven linear FPS that offers: High intensity FPS gameplay with no slowdowns Captivating story of Red Army soldier trying to defend his motherland High variety of weapons including: molotovs, shotguns, snipers, submachine guns and more Cinematic cutscenes
